ApexNet Hexxit SMP


Server Address: apexnet.ga


Get Hexxit




Guide: Installing Hexxit


Step 1
: Download and run Hexxit.exe (the above)




Step 2
: Click Extract




Done!
 You can run Hexxit from your desktop anytime.




Step 3
: Change USERNAME to your ApexNet username




Step 4
: Save and Launch




Step 5
: Click Play!


Make sure your launcher is set to Hexxit and says 1.5.2-BLAH.




Step 6
: Have a root beer and enjoy!




Support


If you don't have 61 mods loaded, can't install Hexxit, or you are having trouble
with our launcher, contact nexus331@gmail.com.
